name: Ball Joint Doll
description:
Ball Joint Doll

An extremely idiot move you say? Sure, why not waste 1 dollar 40 on hugging face cause you're BORED.

A warning: I have 0 interest in re-testing this, so all prompts and images are from the HF space alone, and i've saved my prompts from each run roughly. So please DO NOT ask for more examples than what is provided.

YES at some stage, you will be able to have a safe-tensors, I am not that mean.

I am not going to do much more with this model, it's not my fault what you do with it.

No ball joint dolls were harmed, and no barbies are in the data ,get your mind out of the gutter! LOL

We stream a lot of our testing on twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/duskfallcrew

any chance you can spare a coffee or three? https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want custom LoRA OR MODEL trained an option will become available on the Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

No sample prompt - look at the images until i can get back to testing this!

LORA & EMBEDS LIST HERE: https://civitai.com/models/20562/epic-mix-anime-realism-and-nsfw-support

Sample prompt:"

  1. vjt (masterpiece, best quality, perfect eyes), (green eyes) , (best photograph, extreme light and shadow, perfect composition)1girl, solo, ball joint doll, porcelain doll, red hair, green eyes, kimono

  2. vjt , extremely beautiful doll, (masterpiece, best quality, perfect eyes), (green eyes) , (best photograph, extreme light and shadow, perfect composition)1girl, solo,brown hair, green eyes, (japanese clothing), (golden ratio), (high quality, best illustration), dynamic angle, wide shot

  3. vjt , extremely beautiful doll, green eyes, rainbow hair, (masterpiece, best quality, perfect eyes), (green eyes) , (best photograph, extreme light and shadow, perfect composition)1girl, solo,brown hair, green eyes, (japanese clothing), (golden ratio), (high quality, best illustration), dynamic angle, wide shot

Third one the API has not let me see the images, but it's an example prompt.

No models were used to test this, it's a 1.5 base finetune.

Merge at will.
